    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver being sold as-is. This is a usable, presentable car, but it shows its age with noticeable cosmetic wear, imperfections in the finish, and an interior that is serviceable rather than especially fresh. It runs and can be enjoyed as-is, though buyers should expect typical older-vehicle needs and some deferred maintenance or minor mechanical sorting. A solid option for someone who wants an entry-level example without paying top-market money, but it is not a mint or fully restored car.",
