    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone looking for an inexpensive daily driver, a project, or a dependable backup car without a big upfront cost. Priced to reflect its condition and offer strong value, it\u2019s a practical opportunity for anyone who wants usable transportation at a budget-friendly price point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts conversations the same way it starts mornings\u2014with character. A great option for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone after a simple project. Priced fairly for what it is, and sold honestly. If you want something affordable and approachable, this could be the one.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid project with great bones and a surprisingly eager drivetrain. Starts, runs, and delivers the kind of analog feel enthusiasts appreciate, with a chassis that still feels composed and a powertrain that pulls cleanly for its age. Not a showroom piece, but it has the right foundation for a budget build, daily beater, or weekend wrenching platform. A straightforward, mechanical car with character, good parts potential, and plenty of life left for the next owner willing to give it some attention.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Sold as-is, but ready to move. Great deal for someone who wants low upfront cost.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its steel and plenty of road ahead for the right owner. It has that honest, broken-in character some buyers actively seek\u2014an ideal candidate for a budget daily, a hands-on project, or a dependable backup to keep moving life forward. The body and cabin show the kind of lived-in personality you\u2019d expect from a well-traveled machine, but underneath it all is a vehicle with presence, purpose, and the chance to be something rewarding for someone who sees its potential. If you want affordable wheels with grit, charm, and room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
