      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle offers straightforward value for the budget-conscious buyer. It shows its age cosmetically, but it presents as a practical option for daily use, a second vehicle, or a project opportunity. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering solid utility, this is a great chance to get into a vehicle without overspending.",
      "price": 6950.0,
